        "title": "Letter to Owen Barfield (7 May 1949)",
        "printedIn": "Walter Hooper, “‘Warnie’s Problem’: An Introduction to a Letter from C.S. Lewis to Owen Barfield,” <i>Journal of Inklings Studies</i>",
        "issueOrVolume": "vol. 5, no. 1",
